| `ModelRegistry` | Knows how to fetch API keys and headers for each provider. |
| `SettingsManager` | Loads user, project, and global settings. |
| `SessionManager` | Persists sessions on disk, supports branching, compaction. |
| `ResourceLoader` | Loads extensions, skills, prompt templates, and themes. |
| `StreamFn` | Wraps the chosen provider SDK (Anthropic, OpenAI…) and returns a *stream* of `AssistantMessageEvent`s. |

